data.description: NEW PRICE!!!! 1638 16th Street SE is a completely, gut renovated, turn-key two unit apartment building directly across the street from Anacostia high school. Renovated in 2020, the building consists of two apartment units. Both are three bedrooms and each unit as one full and one half bathroom. Originally built for Section 8 vouchers, it can deliver vacant and or with pre screened section 8 tenants.   The building will gross $52,992 Building has no trash fees Each unit earns $2,208 with utilities per month Two potential parking spaces in rear Additional FAR to be captured  Anacostia has been one of our region's high land appreciation zip codes over the past few years with the median home price in Anacostia, increasing 14.5% compared to 2019.  With the development of Phase II of The Wharf, St. Elizabeth's and other private and public developments, we expect to continue to see significant appreciation and value in SE.
